narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: weaknesses: the professor. very narcissistic and unprofessional. egotistical and can be mean.

Strength: films were very interesting and it was really cool to have the filmmakers visit. Weakness: the class lacked structure, incredibly difficult to be in for almost 2 hours, also only received feedback on one work done in class. Professor Harris was not good at facilitating discussion, but the students in the class had very insightful comments and I learned a lot from them. Professor Harris also assumed everyone had knowledge of how to read and critique film, even though many of us told him it was our first film class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: yes if it was taught by another professor
